title: A $29 Million Paycheck Makes Leonardo DiCaprio The Highest-Paid Male Oscar Nominee

meta_data.description: The Revenant may not be the movie Leonardo DiCaprio deserves an Academy Award for, but he is currently odds-on favorite to finally win the Oscar for Best Actor at this Sunday's show.
